dataIdInfo.idAbs: This data layer represents zoning for Manitowoc County, Wisconsin in 2014[This map data layer represents the zoning district boundaries for the towns in Manitowoc County, Wisconsin that have adopted the county's zoning ordinance.]
dataIdInfo.idPurp:
This layer is intended for reference and mapping purposes, and may be used for basic applications such as viewing, querying, and map output production, or to provide a basemap to support graphical overlays and analysis with other spatial data.
[The zoning map data layer is an integral part of the planning and zoning data in the Manitowoc County GIS. The data are used in case review, enforcement, and long range planning. GIS data layers are accessed by personnel in many county departments for cartographic use and general spatial analysis. They are not intended for legal, survey, or other related uses.]
